{"tid":376091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天鴿襲澳門】澳門取消下周國際煙花比賽匯等活動集中資源善後","createTime":"2017-08-26T19:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T03:40:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a56274075e993cf31e500e0be7c1130721fbf5ea","tid":376091,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170826/photo/bkn-20170826192019585-0826_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170826200552\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170826192019585-0826_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170826200552&h=11238f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳門風災後全城悲慟，澳門政府宣布，即日(26日)起取消近期一系列公眾、節慶、文娛康體及交流活動，包括第29屆澳門國際煙花比賽匯演及相關活動，以集中資源和力量，處理颱風「天鴿」的善後工作。<br />\n<br />\n一年一度的澳門國際煙花比賽匯演，原定今年9月2日至10月1日分5個周末或周日舉行，5天活動合共有10場煙花表演，今年10支比賽隊伍分別來自澳洲、奧地利、英國、法國、日本、菲律賓、德國、意大利、葡萄牙和中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170826/bkn-20170826192019585-0826_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170826%2Fbkn-20170826192019585-0826_00822_001.html&d=R%2Fp%2FYRGdOAPzTNHfut%2Bn2Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7f0ed050\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170826/bkn-20170826192019585-0826_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e581776887006ea888ef1b22231d0df0e55d883","tid":376091,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cVW0PTc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcVW0PTc.png&h=1f2dc39f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2993e344a3cd4a6e68c185d1f8b748c1f61a6cdf","tid":376091,"uid":41245,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:13:44.000Z","msg":"香港都要默哀澳門呀！取消埋香港個中國國慶啦<br />\n姐妹城市嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地都好哀傷㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class